articles.title: Satwiksairaj Rankireddy-Chirag Shetty Win Historic Gold In Badminton Asia Championships - NDTV Sports
articles.description: Satwiksairaj Rankireddy-Chirag Shetty won a historic men's doubles gold medal In Badminton Asia Championships.
articles.content: Star doubles pair of Satwiksairaj Rankireddy and Chirag Shetty on Sunday broke a 58-year-old drought, becoming the first Indians after Dinesh Khanna to be crowned champions at the Asia badminton Cham… [+4036 chars]
